1-850-520-4757 or 850-598-6024
Sapphire Island Camping and RV Resort
5687 US Hwy 331 South
DeFuniak Springs, Florida  32435
Success! Message received.
Send
If coming from I-10:
Take exit 85 South at the DeFuniak Springs exit from I-10. Once you exit, travel South on Hwy. 331 towards Freeport. The park is located on the LEFT 1 mile past the Hospital.
If coming from highway 331 or 83:
Travel south to 331 S. Drive through the city of DeFuniak Springs towards Freeport. The park is located on the LEFT 1 mile past the Hospital.
Note: Sapphire Island RV park & campground entrance is on highway 331. The entrance is on your Left. So start to slow down once you see the white church. You will turn left at the 2nd left turn lane. You will see a 2 story log cabin.
